PAPA v. RINI. (Supreme Court, Appellate Division, First Department. March 17, 1916.) Proceeding by Pasquaie Papa against Michael O. Rini. Heard on motions. Motions denied. See, also, 157 N. Y. Supp. 1079.

Argued before CLARKE, P. X, and DOWLING, SMITH, PAGE, and DAVIS, JJ.

PER CURIAM.

Motions denied, without costs. Orders filed.
